        <h2 className="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Plan Your 2-5 Pages</h2>
        <p className="text-slate-600">Not sure which pages you need? Describe your idea, and our AI will suggest the perfect structure.</p>
